725800f-a.title: Queens: 113th Place - 76th Road
725800f-a.text:
113th Place, south from 76th Road. Shown, too, is the lower
end of Flushing Meadow Park viewing southeastward toward Grand
Central Parkway and Union Turnpike.
February 10, 1937
P. L. Sperr

725801f-a.title: Queens: 113th Place - 76th Road
725801f-a.text:
113th Place, north from 76th Road, showing the thoroughfare
winding its course on the crest of the embankment. On the extreme
Nright is Grand Central Parkway running through Flushing Meadow
Park.
February 10, 1937
P. L. Sperr
